  08 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> django-ldapdb-0.3.2.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug 540290

  06 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> django-ldapdb-0.3.2.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 540290

*django-ldapdb-0.3.2 (09 Jul 2014)

  09 Jul 2014; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> +django-ldapdb-0.3.2.ebuild,
  -django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424-r1.ebuild,
  -django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424.ebuild, -django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20130712.ebuild:
  drop py2.6, switch SRC_URI to pypi, drop IUSE examples, doc due to absence of
  content in tarball's source, based on patch by D. Bogomolov from Bug #516688,
  fixes said bug, rm most old snapshots

*django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20130921 (21 Sep 2013)

  21 Sep 2013; Theo Chatzimichos <tampakrap@gentoo.org>
  +django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20130921.ebuild:
  New snapshot, taken from gentoo/django-ldapdb fork, okupy_v2 branch Simplify
  ebuild Add mockldap dependency

*django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20130712 (16 Jul 2013)

  16 Jul 2013; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org>
  +django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20130712.ebuild, -django-ldapdb-0.2.0_p20130712.ebuild:
  Fix version number; 0.2.0 has never been released and setup.py says 0.1.0.

  13 Jul 2013; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org>
  django-ldapdb-0.2.0_p20130712.ebuild:
  Unrestrict test phase, disable test set demanding an ldap server to which to
  connect

*django-ldapdb-0.2.0_p20130712 (12 Jul 2013)

  12 Jul 2013; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org>
  +django-ldapdb-0.2.0_p20130712.ebuild, django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424.ebuild:
  Making a manufactured bump by way of a fresh snapshot

*django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424-r1 (12 Jul 2013)

  12 Jul 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424-r1.ebuild:
  Convert to distutils-r1. Drop tests as they require LDAP server.

  14 Nov 2012; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Updating maintainer, metadata.xml

  20 May 2012; Theo Chatzimichos <tampakrap@gentoo.org>
  django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424.ebuild:
  pypy && jython restricted; django -> RDEPEND; test phase set to use use
  django's manage.py, test examples excluded from tests

  25 Apr 2012; Theo Chatzimichos <tampakrap@gentoo.org>
  django-ldapdb-0.1.0_p20120424.ebuild:
